). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/112/95/s428/a/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 112–95, § 428(a)(1)","children":[],"tail":", inserted “for each fiscal year” before “is authorized” and substituted “under this subchapter” for “under this subchapter for each fiscal year”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/112/95/s428/a/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 112–95, § 428(a)(2)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “, $143,000,000 for fiscal year 2012, $118,000,000 for fiscal year 2013, $107,000,000 for fiscal year 2014, and $93,000,000 for fiscal year 2015” for “and $54,699,454 for the period beginning on "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2011-10-01"},"text":"October 1, 2011","children":[],"tail":", and ending on "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2012-02-17"},"text":"February 17, 2012","children":[],"tail":",”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/112/91"},"text":"Pub. L. 112–91","children":[],"tail":" substituted “and $54,699,454 for the period beginning on "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2011-10-01"},"text":"October 1, 2011","children":[],"tail":", and ending on "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2012-02-17"},"text":"February 17, 2012","children":[],"tail":",” for “and $50,309,016 for the period beginning on "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2011-10-01"},"text":"October 1, 2011","children":[],"tail":", and ending on "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2012-01-31"},"text":"January 31, 2012","children":[],"tail":",”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/112/95/s428/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 112–95, § 428(b)","children":[],"tail":", amended subsec. (b) generally. Prior to amendment, text read as follows: “Notwithstanding any other provision of law, moneys credited to the account established under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t49/s45303/a"},"text":"section 45303(a) of this title","children":[],"tail":", including the funds derived from fees imposed under the authority contained in "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t49/s45301/a"},"text":"section 45301(a) of this title","children":[],"tail":", shall be used to carry out the essential air service program under this subchapter. Notwithstanding "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t49/s47114/g"},"text":"section 47114(g) of this title","children":[],"tail":", any amounts from those fees that are not obligated or expended at the end of the fiscal year for the purpose of funding the essential air service program under this subchapter shall be made available to the Administration for use in improving rural air safety under subchapter I of chapter 471 of this title and shall be used exclusively for projects at rural airports under this subchapter.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/112/95/s428/c"},"text":"Pub. L. 112–95, § 428(c)","children":[],"tail":", added subsec. (c)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2011—Subsec. (a)(2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/112/30"},"text":"Pub. L. 112–30","children":[],"tail":" substituted “there is authorized to be appropriated out of the Airport and Airway Trust Fund (established under section 9502 of the Internal Revenue Code of 1986) $150,000,000 for fiscal year 2011 and $50,309,016 for the period beginning on "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2011-10-01"},"text":"October 1, 2011","children":[],"tail":", and ending on "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2012-01-31"},"text":"January 31, 2012","children":[],"tail":",” for “there is authorized to be appropriated $77,000,000 for each fiscal year”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2003—Subsec. (a)(2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/176/s404/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–176, § 404(1)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “$77,000,000” fo